PrecisEnactment of an ORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN LANDS IN THE NORTHWEST TERRITORIES (SALT RIVER FIRST NATION, N.W.T.) - which provides for the withdrawal from disposal, until August 31, 2006, of some 41,942 hectares of land in the Northwest Territories, near Fort Smith, in order to facilitate the settlement of land claims made by the Salt River First Nation.
RegistrationRegistration: SI / 2001-0108 Publication Date: 2001-11-07

precis:
Enactment of an ORDER RESPECTING THE WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN
LANDS IN THE NORTHWEST TERRITORIES (SALT RIVER FIRST NATION, N.W.T.) -
which provides for the withdrawal from disposal, until August 31, 2006, of
some 41,942 hectares of land in the Northwest Territories, near Fort Smith,
in order to facilitate the settlement of land claims made by the
Salt River First Nation.
